# Whitelist: only harness scripts, decoders, and patches are tracked.
# Everything else here is environment/artifacts: ares/aresroot/ccache build
# trees, relay-target binaries, np64out logs+screenshots, campaign outputs —
# and ROMs (*.z64), which contain Nintendo assets and must NEVER be committed.
*
!/*.sh
!/*.py
!/ares_netpak.patch
!/.gitignore
!/README.md
!/README_HUMAN.md
